      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_136786be17c419804718193764bfa601">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arranged chronologically and by material type.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_088729c77aa99c787cc73dd88be93385">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection consists of documents, photographs, clippings, and memorabilia concerning the building of the Yale Bowl. A small quantity of material documents its later use.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
